Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.30,0:00:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家，卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.70,0:00:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀看的時候要注意保持屋內亮度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.00,0:00:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.30,0:00:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，那麼，那麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.40,0:00:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家遇到第一次的時候\N都會非常緊張的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.80,0:00:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望自己能夠好好幹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.00,0:00:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我這回第一次演主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.30,0:00:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很努力的練習了\N可為什麼會招到不滿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.50,0:00:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，完全不明白\N不明白，不明白！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.20,0:02:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人魚公主的主角\N由苗木野空和阿娜哈特出演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.90,0:02:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的演出雖然\N只是為期二周的特別公演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.00,0:02:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過宣傳工作一定要做好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表現出點主角的熱情來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就象現在在拍電影的蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.10,0:02:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天是宣傳海報的攝影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後天是宣傳手冊的攝影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後參加有線電視的宣傳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.40,0:02:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不 好像有點……時間太……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.10,0:02:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神點，你是主角啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.30,0:02:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主角……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打算發呆到什麼時候？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.00,0:02:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.00,0:02:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要開始拍了，擺個姿勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.10,0:03:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人魚公主表情豐富點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.30,0:03:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王子再靠近點人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.40,0:03:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能表現的浪漫點呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.10,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.70,0:03:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.20,0:03:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜真帥啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.40,0:03:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都有點暈暈乎乎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.90,0:03:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺很不錯哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.50,0:03:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.10,0:03:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的話……\N倒是希望她能愛上水母
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.00,0:03:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.70,0:03:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.70,0:03:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.70,0:03:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我的話，一定會成功的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.50,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別在意她們的話，空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是憑實力得到角色的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.90,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，我不在意這些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.30,0:03:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我來說重要的是\N把人魚公主演的象蕾拉小姐一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.30,0:03:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，電話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.70,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電話？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.70,0:03:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.70,0:03:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.10,0:04:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，雖然是特別公演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.40,0:04:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是第一次做主角呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.70,0:04:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，沒問題的，別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.40,0:04:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.50,0:04:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽很開心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，但是有點擔心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.60,0:04:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.70,0:04:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次公演嘛\N是擔心空會不會亂來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.20,0:04:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.00,0:04:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易才得到和\N蕾拉小姐一樣的角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.10,0:04:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然要努力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.00,0:04:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.10,0:04:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個拿來了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.80,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，給
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.40,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就想再看一遍\N蕾拉小姐的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.00,0:04:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來表演就沒問題了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.20,0:04:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，太高興了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.20,0:04:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也很想看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空演的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.40,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐演的人魚公主好棒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.50,0:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼華麗又動人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.20,0:05:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太厲害了 觀眾都那麼感動的流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.60,0:05:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難怪卡萊多劇團的\N《人魚公主》會那麼出名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.40,0:05:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想演出那樣的人魚公主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊？夫魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看你那麼心浮氣躁的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.90,0:05:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣行嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.60,0:05:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頑固者的逆位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.20,0:05:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏向哪一邊的話什麼都將會失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.30,0:05:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微讓一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾也把你\N那種熱情的目光投向我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.10,0:05:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.60,0:05:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.90,0:06:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一天就滿座哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.30,0:06:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.50,0:06:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.60,0:06:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還以為不是蕾拉小姐的表演\N大家不來看了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.50,0:06:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.50,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期待你的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.20,0:06:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.00,0:06:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.90,0:06:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常優雅的表演啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.10,0:06:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太象蕾拉小姐了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.10,0:06:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.40,0:07:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！太棒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.70,0:07:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,乾杯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.60,0:07:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空真是演的太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.50,0:08:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，完美的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.70,0:08:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空不來嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.30,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，不知道她怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.50,0:08:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難得莎拉小姐來\N為我們第一天表演慶祝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.60,0:08:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算了\N空的一份我們來乾杯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉小姐不是一直在乾杯嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.50,0:08:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天一定要讓觀眾感動得流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.80,0:08:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.70,0:08:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.40,0:08:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾比第一天少多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表演沒有失誤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.90,0:08:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且演出本身也很成功
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.60,0:08:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來，空呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.70,0:08:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.70,0:08:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.70,0:08:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雅格尼斯先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我對你很失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.00,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話\N還是讓蕾拉再演比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.40,0:09:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來是我看走眼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.00,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我雖然不及蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.40,0:09:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是已經很努力地\N在接近她的表演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.00,0:09:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會對你失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.90,0:09:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把蕾拉叫回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.60,0:09:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是蕾拉還在拍電影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.40,0:09:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就等她拍完了\N立刻讓她和空交換角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.20,0:09:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下，雅格尼斯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事\N明白了嗎？空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.80,0:09:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,健，這個是昨天的意見調查？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.60,0:09:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.00,0:09:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是新的演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.80,0:09:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是好像蕾拉小姐一樣的優秀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.00,0:09:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,表演很出色，像是另一位蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.30,0:10:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是希望能夠看到\N新的“人魚公主”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.00,0:10:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒有壞話\N可是都說是蕾拉小姐……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.30,0:10:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空的表演人魚公主沒有問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.10,0:10:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不能夠讓人感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.20,0:10:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為我在模仿蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.60,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想完美的體現\N蕾拉小姐創造的人魚公主的形象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.30,0:10:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，空不是蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.40,0:10:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偏向哪一邊的話什麼都將會失去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.90,0:10:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我成了蕾拉第二了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，要開演了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.20,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣的心情\N我怎麼能表演呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.80,0:10:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白，該怎麼表演才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.50,0:10:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是，沒有你的話就不能開幕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.10,0:10:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快去！你是主角啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.70,0:11:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很少見你這麼嚴肅的說話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.70,0:11:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為主角誰都會遇到困難的障礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.90,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很苦惱、很苦惱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很痛苦\N但是不超越這道障礙的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.10,0:11:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不能真正的融入角色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.40,0:11:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼演？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.60,0:11:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼演好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.80,0:11:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.50,0:11:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.10,0:11:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.60,0:11:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.10,0:11:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天的表演糟透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.60,0:12:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種道歉對觀眾可是行不通的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.00,0:12:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觀眾不是特地來看\N失敗的演出的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.00,0:12:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.60,0:12:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我希望明天不要再失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.20,0:12:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.60,0:12:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以，一起來想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.70,0:12:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.40,0:12:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的人魚公主？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.50,0:12:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還是不明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.60,0:12:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會對你失望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.40,0:12:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，一起來想\N大家從來沒有看過的表演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.30,0:12:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從來沒有看過的表演吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你們 阿娜、美亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.50,0:12:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.00,0:12:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家是通過看表演\N瞭解主角的心情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.40,0:12:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我自己都沒有理解的話\N怎麼可能向觀眾傳遞呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是空的人魚公主\N應該是什麼樣的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先體會一下\N人魚公主的感覺吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.70,0:12:51.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人魚的感覺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼好主意？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.10,0:12:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.90,0:12:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.90,0:13:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在水裏想吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.50,0:13:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是“人魚”嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，還在努力嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.30,0:13:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能為你做的也只有這點了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.00,0:13:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，健
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“啊”什麼呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼呢？空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.30,0:13:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在可不是玩的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.80,0:13:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是人魚就應該是開開心心的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海裏這麼漂亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.20,0:13:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一天下來也不需要上課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.80,0:13:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.90,0:13:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.00,0:13:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有愛刁難人的傢伙在呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可也不是這麼回事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.70,0:13:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那種環境下長大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.40,0:13:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是開朗的\N健康的、純真的女孩子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是人魚公主是悲劇人物啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.10,0:13:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,演成這樣的女孩好嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.80,0:13:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光想是沒用的，總之試試看啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.80,0:14:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼搞笑的人魚公主\N還是第一次看見呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.40,0:14:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主角這樣子演不是太奇怪了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.90,0:14:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太奇怪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.60,0:14:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨，請走好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.00,0:14:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.60,0:14:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問，您覺得\N今天的人魚公主怎麼樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.60,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我真實的感想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.60,0:14:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺是個朝氣蓬勃\N相當可愛的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.70,0:14:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和最後跳入瀑布的情節配不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.60,0:14:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺上前後不相應啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.20,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.40,0:14:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐演的\N人魚公主一定會更優雅些吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.90,0:14:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，謝謝光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.70,0:14:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以直接問觀眾呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是不問怎麼知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.70,0:15:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光自己一個人想是想不明白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.40,0:15:06.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，有點進步了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和蕾拉小姐的人魚小姐不一樣了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.20,0:15:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，的確是有點了空的個性了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.60,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.60,0:15:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得現在的……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.70,0:15:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天的表演是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.80,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那種人魚公主嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.50,0:15:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然改變成那樣\N搞的我們措手不及
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.80,0:15:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得到誰的允許了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.20,0:15:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.30,0:15:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只想表演和蕾拉小姐\N不一樣的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.80,0:15:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有必要這麼做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.40,0:15:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有二周的時間而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.30,0:15:38.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之，不要給我們製造混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.30,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.40,0:15:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們有點自以為是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.70,0:15:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造成了表演的混亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.00,0:15:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，不是你們的錯\N是我……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.20,0:15:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空沒有錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.00,0:15:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是大家一下子\N沒有能夠接受這樣的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.70,0:16:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公演還是要繼續的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要完成人們能夠接受的\N人魚公主就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.80,0:16:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊，不是只有二周了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.50,0:16:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是還有二周呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.30,0:16:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這麼半途而廢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.60,0:16:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要盡力的創作出\N我的人魚公主來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.60,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.10,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，這是什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公演期間\N我就保持人魚公主的樣子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.70,0:16:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和蕾拉小姐不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.70,0:16:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法精心設計之後再表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.10,0:16:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我只能用\N親身體驗角色的內心世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.20,0:16:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.60,0:16:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空，還是不要勉強了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直以魚尾的形式生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.70,0:16:50.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不會有什麼感受吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.60,0:16:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直以魚尾生活的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.30,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然有了腳的話\N可能會摔跤的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.40,0:17:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然找了很多人魚公主的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.10,0:17:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可還是不明白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說哪方面呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人魚公主是因為愛上了王子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.60,0:17:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才會犧牲自己的嗓音\N而獲得了人類的樣子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.50,0:17:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為什麼王子弄錯了\N救命恩人，她卻不說呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.50,0:17:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為不能說話啊\N那是沒辦法的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.30,0:17:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的是沒有辦法嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.70,0:17:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該還有其他的方法吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.30,0:17:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換作我的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.20,0:17:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是真心喜歡的人\N我一定不會就這麼簡單的放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.40,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是怎麼做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.10,0:17:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如聽聽大家的意見吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.00,0:17:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼人魚公主\N不表達自己的感情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.60,0:17:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.50,0:17:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能說話的情況\N不是和我們的舞臺表演類似嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.80,0:17:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們可以\N用肢體語言來表達
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.70,0:18:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，你說的問題\N到目前為止還從來沒有考慮過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確或許現在的觀眾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.50,0:18:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不能夠接受人魚公主\N就這麼默默的離去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.80,0:18:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就大聲的叫喊\N“是我救了你”怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.40,0:18:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼鄰國公主也大膽示愛呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.80,0:18:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那很不錯啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是即使如此\N王子也想不起來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.10,0:18:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼人魚公主怎麼辦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.40,0:18:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帶著王子一起跳入水中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,王子也要跳入瀑布嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.80,0:18:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我來演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿娜，那就太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.30,0:18:30.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人互相擁抱跳入瀑布
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.60,0:18:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後王子就想起了\N人魚公主的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.30,0:18:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,HAPPY END（喜劇結局）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.90,0:18:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是人魚公主\N一直以來是個悲劇故事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.60,0:18:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還是覺得\N喜劇結局比悲劇要好些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.30,0:18:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像變成了個挺有趣的劇本啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.90,0:18:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去爭取卡洛斯的認可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.90,0:18:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後我們全力表演好這個劇本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.70,0:19:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我儘快的拍完了片子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.80,0:19:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是雅格尼斯先生聯絡我回來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.00,0:19:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是單單模仿我的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就想演出出人意料\N的人魚公主嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.30,0:19:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子還沒有能力演主角吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是看看再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的賣座率\N也難怪雅格尼斯先生不滿意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.50,0:19:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.00,0:19:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.50,0:19:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人魚公主在試魔法使\N是不是真的能用魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.70,0:19:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.70,0:19:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法使可能是在撒謊呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.70,0:19:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.50,0:20:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看完再說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.20,0:20:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的緞帶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.30,0:20:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想讓王子想起自己的事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.30,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的人魚公主
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個！就是這個！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.60,0:21:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我到目前為止\N一直尋找的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.30,0:21:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多的新星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人魚公主真是可愛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，真有趣
